PN,41401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773911088
OL,3,CWoman, 21, recovering from meningitis
OL,4,Cgives first interview from hospital bed
OL,6,FA woman from Kent who suffered a
OL,7,Fseizure and collapsed after
OL,8,Fcontracting meningitis, has given her
OL,9,Ffirst interview from her hospital bed.
OL,11,FKeeleigh Goodwin, 21, started
OL,12,Fdeveloping symptoms on Friday after
OL,13,Fattending Chemistry nightclub.
OL,15,FShe was rushed to hospital after her
OL,16,Fhousemates called an ambulance.
OL,18,FLuckily she has been treated and is
OL,19,Fnow recovering, but has described it
OL,20,Fas "a scary experience" and said it
OL,21,Fhas changed her outlook on life.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
