FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773911089
OL,3,CWoman, 21, recovering from meningitis
OL,4,Cgives first interview from hospital bed
OL,6,FSpeaking exclusively to ITV Meridian,
OL,7,Fshe said her first symptoms were a
OL,8,Fsore neck.
OL,10,F"I thought perhaps I pulled muscles or
OL,11,Fsomething but later on Friday evening
OL,12,FI was getting in a lot more pain.
OL,14,F"I was getting hot and cold sweats all
OL,15,Fthrough the night in a lot of pain,
OL,16,Fvery stiff to move like it was very
OL,17,Fhard and then the Saturday I woke up
OL,18,Fstill in a lot of pain, still feeling
OL,19,Fthe same.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773911089
OL,3,CWoman, 21, recovering from meningitis
OL,4,Cgives first interview from hospital bed
OL,6,F"Then the vomiting started and that
OL,7,Flasted all throughout the day."
OL,9,FKeeleigh and her mum Khali thought she
OL,10,Fwas suffering from Covid, and said
OL,11,Fthey were shocked after she was
OL,12,Fdiagnosed with meningitis.
OL,14,F"I didn't know much about it because
OL,15,Fyou know it's not really something you
OL,16,Fthink you'd get," Keeligh added.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773911089
OL,3,CWoman, 21, recovering from meningitis
OL,4,Cgives first interview from hospital bed
OL,6,F"Obviously I knew it was quite a
OL,7,Fserious illness, disease, so I've been
OL,8,Fput on a drip of fluids and IV and
OL,9,Fantibiotics for the treatment which is
OL,10,Fmeant to last seven to ten days so I
OL,11,Fhave to remain in hospital in an
OL,12,Fisolated room for that amount of time.
OL,14,F"It's been quite a scary experience -
OL,15,Fthe fact that I almost could have died
OL,16,Fif I hadn't been found or if the
OL,17,Fseizure had happened in my sleep.
OL,19,F"It's definitely changed my outlook of
OL,20,Flife."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773911089
OL,3,CWoman, 21, recovering from meningitis
OL,4,Cgives first interview from hospital bed
OL,6,FKeeleigh is one of more than a dozen
OL,7,Fpeople admitted to hospital with the
OL,8,Fdisease.
OL,10,FTwo students died and 18 more cases
OL,11,Fwere being investigated by the UKHSA
OL,12,Fafter an outbreak of meningitis linked
OL,13,Fto Chemistry nightclub in Canterbury.
OL,15,FThe rollout of a meningitis B vaccine
OL,16,Fto around 5,000 students living on the
OL,17,FUniversity campus has begun on
OL,18,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773911089
OL,3,CWoman, 21, recovering from meningitis
OL,4,Cgives first interview from hospital bed
OL,6,FIn partnership with the UK Health
OL,7,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA), the
OL,8,Funiversity is rolling out vaccines to
OL,9,Fprotect students and is continuing to
OL,10,Foffer thousands of doses of
OL,11,Fantibiotics to students and staff.
OL,13,FThe university said in a statement the
OL,14,Fjab rollout was "part of our ongoing
OL,15,Fcommitment to offer a swift response
OL,16,Fand reassurance to support Kent
OL,17,Fstudents at this difficult time".
OL,19,FA statement said: "All those affected
OL,20,Fwho are currently linked to the
OL,21,Foutbreak are young adults.
OL,26,@vD@QOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773911089
OL,3,CWoman, 21, recovering from meningitis
OL,4,Cgives first interview from hospital bed
OL,6,F"UKHSA is aware of a baby with
OL,7,Fconfirmed meningococcal group B
OL,8,Finfection who is not currently linked
OL,9,Fto the outbreak but UKHSA will
OL,10,Fcontinue to investigate this case."
OL,12,FCanterbury Christ Church University in
OL,13,FKent has confirmed a case of
OL,14,Fmeningitis among its students.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773911089
OL,3,CWoman, 21, recovering from meningitis
OL,4,Cgives first interview from hospital bed
OL,6,FVice-Chancellor and Principal
OL,7,FProfessor Rama Thirunamachandran at
OL,8,FCanterbury Christchurch University,
OL,9,Fsaid: "The UK Health Security Agency
OL,10,F(UKHSA) has now confirmed one case of
OL,11,Fmeningococcal disease involving a CCCU
OL,12,Fstudent.
OL,14,F"We have reached out to support the
OL,15,Findividual directly. This case is
OL,16,Flinked to the initial cluster
OL,17,Fassociated with Club Chemistry.
OL,19,F"We continue to work with UKHSA,
OL,20,Fpublic health clinicians and other
OL,21,Fpartners on the appropriate response.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1773911089
OL,3,CWoman, 21, recovering from meningitis
OL,4,Cgives first interview from hospital bed
OL,6,F"We recognise this is an anxious and
OL,7,Fchallenging time for the CCCU and
OL,8,Fwider community, and the wellbeing of
OL,9,Four students and staff remains our
OL,10,Fabsolute priority.
OL,12,F"In line with UKHSA advice, our campus
OL,13,Fremains open and core teaching,
OL,14,Flearning and research activities will
OL,15,Fcontinue."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
